nirbandhithanaayi. narthakimaaraavatte, upajeevanathil mattoru maarggavum ariyaanjathinaalaavanam, thangalude nrithathil shringaarathinte athiprasaram varuthaan thudangi. polikali, eashan, *mookkutthi*, chandanam thudangiya puthiya enangal ramgathavatharippichu sthreelambadanmaaraaya kaanikalude preethi pidichu patti, thalkkalam thangalude nilanilppu surakshithamakkaan shramichu. nettiyil chaarthikkodukkunnu. mattoru inamaaya* mookkuthiyilaakatte thante mookkutthi kalanju poyathaayi narthaki vediyil ninnuparayunnu. pinneedu kaanikalude idaykku vannu thiranju thante mookkutthi kandedukkunnu.  mohiniyaattathil vanna eee adapathanam athineyum nartthakikaleyum samoohathinte maanyavedikalil ninnum akatti. kollavarsham 1070-ll erangiya vidyaavinodini enna maasikayiluâ€ pusthakatthil paranjirikkunnu. 1920-kalil korattikkara ennayidathu kaikottikkali padippichu vannirunna kalamozhi krishnamenonte shishyakalil ninnu pazhayannoor chinnammuamma, peringottukurisshi
